{"tid":1787254,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人每次聽到呢一首音樂 都有種想喊嘅衝動?","createTime":"2019-12-17T21:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T15:00:31.000Z","uid":165817,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dbbee5146b04b9a2f2af19f82412c090b3cf839e","tid":1787254,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:18:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qImZFMRkwaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqImZFMRkwaQ&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Buibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=f5638bdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qImZFMRkwaQ</a><br />\n<br />\n相信有返咁上下年紀嘅你<br />\n聽到頭四粒音 已經即刻知道係咩嚟<br />\n已經即刻有啲野喺你腦海彈出嚟<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌嘅旋律好單純 好天真<br />\n亦都代表住嗰一個年代嘅我地<br />\n我地聽住呢首歌嘅時候 無一不是單純天真嘅小朋友<br />\n<br />\n呢首歌攞咗嚟做未白鎮嘅主題音樂<br />\n即係主角嘅屋企<br />\n可能有好多人唔知咩嚟 或者未玩過GBA寶石<br />\n但係只要17年前有玩過嘅<br />\n我相信你地聽到都會有種想喊嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n有少少唔敢聽落去<br />\n好驚會被成長咗嘅自己污染咗首歌<br />\n就算我必須不斷長大<br />\n都想呢首歌永遠保持童年嘅純真<br />\n只要我永遠記住 就已經足夠"},{"pid":"894e0a6f89b0de811ca464deafd31716b091590f","tid":1787254,"uid":124400,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"+1 雖然我只玩過金銀水晶，但聽返D歌總會諗起以前無憂無慮的日子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2667d643116ed43183412a2575d97e715d459605","tid":1787254,"uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"894e0a6f89b0de811ca464deafd31716b091590f","tid":1787254,"uid":124400,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"+1 雖然我只玩過金銀水晶，但聽返D歌總會諗起以前無憂無慮的日子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T21:24:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WuxT9OQ4OyQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWuxT9OQ4OyQ&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Buibpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=ebd4d0ff\" data-auto-link ta